        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ": not throwing off their garments as if preparing to stone Paul (for which Zöckler compares ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Acts 7:58",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", and see Plato, ",
