        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Rep.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", 474 A), for the fact that the Apostle was in the custody of the Romans would have prevented any such purpose. The verb may be used as a frequentative, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "ῥιπτεῖν",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "jactare",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "ῥίπτειν",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "jacere",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", while some of the old grammarians associate with it a suggestion of earnestness or effort, others of contempt, Grimm-Thayer, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "sub v.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " (for the form in LXX ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "cf.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " Dan., Theod., ix., 18, 20). The word here rather means “tossing about their garments,” a manifestation of excitement and uncontrollable rage, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "cf.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
