        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] i.e. the loose upper robe, which could easily be laid aside, and which in such an excitement would interfere with their movements. Compare the conduct of the crowd when our Lord rode into Jerusalem, and also the behaviour of Jehu’s friends, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
