        "text": "ἀνασείων ἐκρότει τὸν Προαιρέσιον",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " \"The proconsul applauded Proairesius the rhetorician by shaking his purple robe,\" Eunapius, 'Life of the Emperor Julian;' \"The whole theatre raved together, and leaped, and shouted, and threw off their garments (",
        "children": []
